      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Scheduler子图搭起来：DESC连到FETCH，FETCH连到FSM，然后FSM分出RD_IF、WR_IF、MON三个分支。RD_IF、WR_IF、MON都是EtcdCluster对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
